The application will have three main panels. A panel on the left, with buttons for
selecting options, a panel in the middle that displays the map, and a pael on the
right that has a textual description of any directions given.

The left panel should include buttons for:
	1. Choosing a starting location
	2. Choosing a destination
	3. Activating GPS directions, from "here" to the destination
	4. Getting directions from start to destination
	
The center panel should display the map, including all roads and geographical
structures. It should highlight the currently selected route if there is one.

THe right panel displays rows of text corresponding to directions on the current
route. It also displays the distance for a particular section of the route.